FBIS4-40446 "drsov116_m_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-116 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 Tajikistan Servicemens' Vehicles Ambushed Servicemens' Vehicles Ambushed LD1606101694 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Tajik 0800 GMT 16 Jun 94 LD1606101694 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network Tajik BFN [Text] Two vehicles carrying servicemen from the Tajik Defense Ministry, who were on their way to Khait village to fulfill their duties, [words indistinct] came under fire last night. As a result, six persons were killed and [word indistinct] were wounded. As a result of these actions Colonel Ramazan Rajabov, deputy defense minister of the Republic of Tajikistan, and Captain S. Kholov, officer of the Defense Ministry's directorate, were killed. The leadership of the Republic's Defense Ministry expresses its deep condolences to the families and close relatives of those killed. The people of the Republic of Tajikistan have lost their [word indistinct] sons in defense of this province and [words indistinct]
